title: Nimrod
brief_description: This is a documentary detailing the evolution of the jet engine. With the use of rare archival footage, we are shown the rapid development of aircraft design, in particular, leading up to and during W.W.II when Germany under Hitler was making dramatic advances with the jet engine. Rated: G
